# Generated UI templates / JSON (pipeline & ticket eval — keep local only)
# Base tickets_latest.json + slate_latest.json are committed stubs for Railway cold deploy.
# Ignore only dated/extra copies so pipeline snapshots do not clutter git.
ui_runner/templates/tickets_latest_*.json
ui_runner/templates/slate_latest_*.json
# ticket_eval_*.html — track in git for Railway/static hosts (served at /grades/<date> and iframe URLs).
# graded_props_YYYY-MM-DD.json under ui_runner/templates/ — keep tracked (Railway serves /grades/props/<date>).
# ui_runner/templates/slate_eval_*.html  # optional: often committed for deploy/CDN

